\mt1 Habakkuk
\is1 Introduction
\ip Te seini baseen, egkabasa ta ka pegpalalahey ni Prupita Habakuk te Magbebaye Manama. Diye mig-ugpe si Habakuk te Huda and nasulat buwa seini baseen te me subla te hen‑em hatus leg‑un (600) te ware pad neetew si Kristu. Ne mig-inse si Habakuk te Manama ke mania te ware din legpari seeye se me karumaan din me matig-Israil migpandeeg-deeg te me meupiya me etew. Migtabak ka Manama egpeuyan sikandin te me sundalu me matig-Babilunya eyew te peglegpad kandan. Te sika timpu, amana ikaaldek ka me sundalu te nasud Babilunya tenged su amana sikandan mabbulut and natalu ran ka nasud te Asirya and Ihiptu. Ware nakasabut si Habakuk ke mania te iling due ka inggimu te Magbebaye Manama. Ne mig-inse sikandin te Manama miggenendue, “Mania te imparuyun-duyunan nu ka me etew kene matinumanen? Ne mania te egpeeneng-eneng ka ke egdereetan dan ka me etew matareng pad kandan?” (1:13). Ne migtabak ka Manama egbulig sikandin te eleg timpu, sasangan pad: “…ka me matareng, egkeuyag mule tenged te pegpalintutuu ran.” (2:4)
\ip The duma baad te seini baseen iyan ka pegtagne te egginguma karereetan te seeye se maddeet etew. Ne minsan egkaaldek si Habakuk egdusaan e te Manama ka Huda, piru migpalintutuu red sikandin egluwasen din ded ka keet-etawan din and egbehayan te kanekal egpakaantus te keyirapan egkeula-ula ran. Mig-impusan ka seini baseen te ulahingen te pegdayan te Magbebaye maresen.
